(4656, 435, 'strong_customer_relationships_section__content', '<p>We’re committed to a standard set of values, strong customer relationships, and meaningful collaboration.</p>\r\n<p>Every tax services firm will tell you they provide quality products, timely reporting, and great communication.  At Meridian, those are just the basic elements of good business. Our focus from the day our firm launched has been on building relationships.  Client service is the motivation behind all our actions to provide nothing less than exceptional value for our clients.</p>'),
