(6899, 517, '_current_tax_laws_heading', 'field_618f7699c20ac'),
(6900, 517, 'current_tax_laws_content', '<p>The Tax Cuts and Jobs Act (TCJA) provides 100% bonus depreciation through the end of 2022. In prior years bonus was only extended to new construction.  The expansion of Bonus depreciation to include acquired properties is creating never before seen benefits.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For eligible properties, every $1M in building cost provides building owners with increased cash flow of $60K to $140K in the first year.</strong></p>'),
(6901, 517, '_current_tax_laws_content', 'field_618f76a7c20ad'),
(6902, 517, 'consider_the_example_heading', 'Consider the example'),
(6903, 517, '_consider_the_example_heading', 'field_618f76edc20ae'),
(6904, 517, 'consider_the_example_content', '<p>Acquisition of $4.3M triple net lease big box retail property  - total reclassification falls on the lower end of the benefit range of a typical retail property.</p>\r\n<p>The cost segregation analysis reallocated 24% into shorter life 5 and 15 year property. The overall cost/benefit ratio is 53 to 1.</p>'),
(6905, 517, '_consider_the_example_content', 'field_618f76fbc20af'),
(6906, 517, 'example_table', '<table class=\"table\">\r\n  <thead>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <th scope=\"col\"></th>\r\n      <th scope=\"col\">Without Cost Segregation</th>\r\n      <th scope=\"col\">Pre-TCJA (no bonus)</th>\r\n      <th scope=\"col\">Post-TCJA (100% bonus)</th>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </thead>\r\n  <tbody>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>1st Year Tax Savings</td>\r\n      <td>$19,295</td>\r\n      <td>$49,549</td>\r\n      <td>$356,569</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    <tr>\r\n      <td>5 Year NPV</td>\r\n      <td>$205,179</td>\r\n      <td>Thornton</td>\r\n      <td>$325,894</td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n  </tbody>\r\n</table>'),
