INSERT INTO `wmeridancep_postmeta` (`meta_id`, `post_id`, `meta_key`, `meta_value`) VALUES
(7614, 655, 'authority_slider_2_content', '<p>We’ve established a strong working relationship in cost segregation with the IRS, earning their respect based on the quality of our studies. In fact, we learned the IRS referred to our lead engineer’s methodology as the authority when they drafted the cost segregation engineering methodology in their 2004 Audit Techniques Guide. </p>\r\n						<p>Meridian clients benefit from our experience, earned from audits with public companies and institutional clients defending their fixed asset classifications for depreciation and future write-offs. </p>'),
(7615, 655, '_authority_slider_2_content', 'field_618fb1590c9bf'),
(7616, 655, 'authority_slider', '3'),
(7617, 655, '_authority_slider', 'field_618fb1270c9bd'),
(7618, 655, 'we_offer_a_complete_audit_trail_heading', 'We offer a complete audit trail –  <span>We offer a complete audit trail – ticked and tied so there is nothing to hide.</span>'),
(7619, 655, '_we_offer_a_complete_audit_trail_heading', 'field_618fb6866e474'),
(7620, 655, 'we_offer_a_complete_audit_trail_content', '<p>Meridian’s engineering methodology provides all the advantages and opportunities that cost segregation allows, in a fully defensible study – the key element when undergoing an IRS audit. And, we’re one of only a handful of firms that offer a comprehensive work paper file and  supporting audit trail.</p>'),
(7621, 655, '_we_offer_a_complete_audit_trail_content', 'field_618fb69e6e475'),
(7622, 655, 'we_take_the_burden_0_image', '654'),
(7623, 655, '_we_take_the_burden_0_image', 'field_618fb7296e477'),
(7624, 655, 'we_take_the_burden_0_title', '1.'),
(7625, 655, '_we_take_the_burden_0_title', 'field_618fb73b6e478'),
(7626, 655, 'we_take_the_burden_0_content', '<p>We take the burden of proof off the taxpayer and CPA by providing details for the entire building– versus cherry-picking assets – in a construction format that’s easy for the IRS to follow under audit.</p>'),
(7627, 655, '_we_take_the_burden_0_content', 'field_618fb7496e479'),
(7628, 655, 'we_take_the_burden_1_image', '653'),
(7629, 655, '_we_take_the_burden_1_image', 'field_618fb7296e477'),
(7630, 655, 'we_take_the_burden_1_title', '2.'),
(7631, 655, '_we_take_the_burden_1_title', 'field_618fb73b6e478'),
(7632, 655, 'we_take_the_burden_1_content', '<p>As a result of our engineering methodology, combined with our tax code, regulatory, and case law expertise, we frequently identify 10% more documentable benefits than our competitors – differentiating our firm from other practices</p>'),
(7633, 655, '_we_take_the_burden_1_content', 'field_618fb7496e479'),
(7634, 655, 'we_take_the_burden', '2'),
(7635, 655, '_we_take_the_burden', 'field_618fb6fc6e476'),
(7636, 655, 'being_the_most_experienced_advantages', '<p>Being the most experienced in our business has its advantages, which we pass on to our clients. With our combination of experience and highly qualified specialists, we provide competitive pricing for projects of all types and sizes, while offering the highest quality product in the industry. Meridian clients appreciate the combination of value and service they receive, leading to their repeat business.</p>'),
(7637, 655, '_being_the_most_experienced_advantages', 'field_618fb76a6e47a'),
