(7781, 678, 'over_our_long_tenure_in_the_industry_heading', 'Over our long tenure in the industry, we’ve helped shape cost segregation on behalf of taxpayers.'),
(7782, 678, '_over_our_long_tenure_in_the_industry_heading', 'field_618f9d7f51f45'),
(7783, 678, 'over_our_long_tenure_in_the_industry_content', '<p>Since the late 1980s, our leadership team has been engaged in construction audits, claims and dispute litigation, and direct dealings with the IRS on landmark tax cases.</p> 					<p>Additionally, our lead engineer is recognized by the U.S. Tax Court as an industry expert witness in cost segregation, and has served as a subject matter expert witness on behalf of taxpayers AND the IRS.</p>'),
(7784, 678, '_over_our_long_tenure_in_the_industry_content', 'field_618f9de451f47'),
(7785, 678, 'our_broad_range_of_industry_heading', 'Our broad range of industry experience includes: '),
(7786, 678, '_our_broad_range_of_industry_heading', 'field_618f9e0b51f48'),
(7787, 678, 'our_broad_range_of_industry_list', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Everything from billion dollar projects to small build-outs</li>\r\n	<li>Classified facility inspection with National Security Clearance </li>\r\n	<li>More than 18,000 studies of every commercial property type in all 50 states, Mexico, Europe, the Middle East, and South America.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(7788, 678, '_our_broad_range_of_industry_list', 'field_618f9e2351f49'),
(7789, 678, 'our_broad_range_of_industry_image', '644'),
(7790, 678, '_our_broad_range_of_industry_image', 'field_618fadec0c9ba'),
(7791, 678, 'our_studies_have_withstood_the_scrutiny_of_heading', 'Our studies have withstood the scrutiny of:'),
(7792, 678, '_our_studies_have_withstood_the_scrutiny_of_heading', 'field_618fae0b0c9bb'),
(7793, 678, 'our_studies_have_withstood_the_scrutiny_of_content', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Over 2,000 combined Revenue Agent Reviews (RARs) with 100% success</li>\r\n	<li>Full audits on completed projects, both pre- and post-2004 Cost Segregation Audit Techniques Guide </li>\r\n	<li>Thousands of CPA reviews</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(7794, 678, '_our_studies_have_withstood_the_scrutiny_of_content', 'field_618fae1a0c9bc'),
(7795, 678, 'authority_slider_0_title', 'The IRS refers <span>to us as The</span> Authority.'),
(7796, 678, '_authority_slider_0_title', 'field_618fb1530c9be'),
(7797, 678, 'authority_slider_0_content', '<p>We’ve established a strong working relationship in cost segregation with the IRS, earning their respect based on the quality of our studies. In fact, we learned the IRS referred to our lead engineer’s methodology as the authority when they drafted the cost segregation engineering methodology in their 2004 Audit Techniques Guide. </p>\r\n						<p>Meridian clients benefit from our experience, earned from audits with public companies and institutional clients defending their fixed asset classifications for depreciation and future write-offs. </p>'),
(7798, 678, '_authority_slider_0_content', 'field_618fb1590c9bf'),
(7799, 678, 'authority_slider_1_title', 'The IRS refers <span>to us as The</span> Authority.'),
(7800, 678, '_authority_slider_1_title', 'field_618fb1530c9be'),
(7801, 678, 'authority_slider_1_content', '<p>We’ve established a strong working relationship in cost segregation with the IRS, earning their respect based on the quality of our studies. In fact, we learned the IRS referred to our lead engineer’s methodology as the authority when they drafted the cost segregation engineering methodology in their 2004 Audit Techniques Guide. </p>\r\n						<p>Meridian clients benefit from our experience, earned from audits with public companies and institutional clients defending their fixed asset classifications for depreciation and future write-offs. </p>'),
(7802, 678, '_authority_slider_1_content', 'field_618fb1590c9bf'),
(7803, 678, 'authority_slider_2_title', 'The IRS refers <span>to us as The</span> Authority.'),
(7804, 678, '_authority_slider_2_title', 'field_618fb1530c9be'),
(7805, 678, 'authority_slider_2_content', '<p>We’ve established a strong working relationship in cost segregation with the IRS, earning their respect based on the quality of our studies. In fact, we learned the IRS referred to our lead engineer’s methodology as the authority when they drafted the cost segregation engineering methodology in their 2004 Audit Techniques Guide. </p>\r\n						<p>Meridian clients benefit from our experience, earned from audits with public companies and institutional clients defending their fixed asset classifications for depreciation and future write-offs. </p>'),
(7806, 678, '_authority_slider_2_content', 'field_618fb1590c9bf'),
