(7809, 678, 'we_offer_a_complete_audit_trail_heading', 'We offer a complete audit trail – <span>ticked and tied so there is nothing to hide.</span>'),
(7810, 678, '_we_offer_a_complete_audit_trail_heading', 'field_618fb6866e474'),
(7811, 678, 'we_offer_a_complete_audit_trail_content', '<p>Meridian’s engineering methodology provides all the advantages and opportunities that cost segregation allows, in a fully defensible study – the key element when undergoing an IRS audit. And, we’re one of only a handful of firms that offer a comprehensive work paper file and  supporting audit trail.</p>'),
(7812, 678, '_we_offer_a_complete_audit_trail_content', 'field_618fb69e6e475'),
(7813, 678, 'we_take_the_burden_0_image', '654'),
(7814, 678, '_we_take_the_burden_0_image', 'field_618fb7296e477'),
(7815, 678, 'we_take_the_burden_0_title', '1.'),
(7816, 678, '_we_take_the_burden_0_title', 'field_618fb73b6e478'),
(7817, 678, 'we_take_the_burden_0_content', '<p>We take the burden of proof off the taxpayer and CPA by providing details for the entire building– versus cherry-picking assets – in a construction format that’s easy for the IRS to follow under audit.</p>'),
(7818, 678, '_we_take_the_burden_0_content', 'field_618fb7496e479'),
