(7822, 678, '_we_take_the_burden_1_title', 'field_618fb73b6e478'),
(7823, 678, 'we_take_the_burden_1_content', '<p>As a result of our engineering methodology, combined with our tax code, regulatory, and case law expertise, we frequently identify 10% more documentable benefits than our competitors – differentiating our firm from other practices</p>'),
(7824, 678, '_we_take_the_burden_1_content', 'field_618fb7496e479'),
(7825, 678, 'we_take_the_burden', '2'),
(7826, 678, '_we_take_the_burden', 'field_618fb6fc6e476'),
(7827, 678, 'being_the_most_experienced_advantages', '<p>Being the most experienced in our business has its advantages, which we pass on to our clients. With our combination of experience and highly qualified specialists, we provide competitive pricing for projects of all types and sizes, while offering the highest quality product in the industry. Meridian clients appreciate the combination of value and service they receive, leading to their repeat business.</p>'),
