(7864, 681, '_construction_0_title', 'field_618f9058a01d9'),
(7865, 681, 'construction_0_content', '<p>This proactive approach allows our experts to identify potential tax savings, incentives and strategies in the design-build stage resulting in a better documentation trail and tax-related Value Engineering opportunities. Set up a consultation to uncover the tax savings in the architecture of your next project.</p>'),
(7866, 681, '_construction_0_content', 'field_618f905ea01da'),
