(7892, 681, '_our_solutions_are_tailored_heading', 'field_618f9130a01e1'),
(7893, 681, 'our_solutions_are_tailored_content', '<p>If a business is not currently profitable or the property is a short-term hold, it may not make sense to do a study or it may make sense to wait a few years. Our clients trust us because we are firm in our commitment to do what is right for the client.</p>'),
