(8354, 728, 'current_tax_laws_heading', 'Current tax laws make Cost Segregation even more beneficial.'),
(8355, 728, '_current_tax_laws_heading', 'field_618f7699c20ac'),
(8356, 728, 'current_tax_laws_content', '<p>The Tax Cuts and Jobs Act (TCJA) provides 100% bonus depreciation through the end of 2022. In prior years bonus was only extended to new construction.  The expansion of Bonus depreciation to include acquired properties is creating never before seen benefits.</p>\r\n<p><strong>For eligible properties, every $1M in building cost provides building owners with increased cash flow of $60K to $140K in the first year.</strong></p>'),
