INSERT INTO `wmeridancep_postmeta` (`meta_id`, `post_id`, `meta_key`, `meta_value`) VALUES
(11900, 822, 'r&d_tax_credit_studies_content', '<p>We’ve delivered studies for Fortune 500 companies, mid-sized companies, and small businesses. Our expertise has been shaped by experience managing hundreds of R&D tax credit studies and R&D state and federal audits, many by conference appeals. Meridian’s lead legal strategist has influenced the code and regulations, expanding qualifications. </p>'),
(11901, 822, '_r&d_tax_credit_studies_content', 'field_617e280199a32'),
(11902, 822, 'get_started_url', '#'),
(11903, 822, '_get_started_url', 'field_617e285d99a33'),
(11904, 822, 'receive_every_benefit_title', 'Receive every benefit you qualify for'),
(11905, 822, '_receive_every_benefit_title', 'field_617e29d099a34'),
(11906, 822, 'receive_every_benefit_sub_title', ''),
(11907, 822, '_receive_every_benefit_sub_title', 'field_617e29d699a35'),
(11908, 822, 'receive_every_benefit_description', '<p>We take the time to get to know our clients’ business, ask the right questions, and document our results, saving more than $70 million in tax payments annually, with a comprehensive approach to qualifying and quantifying credits. </p>\r\n\r\n<p>A lot of providers cut corners to increase profit margins at the client’s expense. For example, instead of identifying and documenting 3 to 5 of the biggest projects conducted by a client in a prior year, we uncover every qualifying activity. </p>\r\n'),
(11909, 822, '_receive_every_benefit_description', 'field_617e29e699a36'),
(11910, 822, 'meridian_finance_has_completed_over_title', 'Meridian finance has <span>completed over</span>'),
(11911, 822, '_meridian_finance_has_completed_over_title', 'field_617e2a8699a37'),
(11912, 822, 'case_studies', '<span>500+</span> Case studies'),
(11913, 822, '_case_studies', 'field_617e2a9e99a38'),
(11914, 822, 'case_studies_image', '195'),
(11915, 822, '_case_studies_image', 'field_617e2aa799a39'),
(11916, 822, 'don’t_let_tax_savings_go_unclaimed', 'Don’t let tax savings go unclaimed.'),
(11917, 822, '_don’t_let_tax_savings_go_unclaimed', 'field_617e2ad299a3a'),
(11918, 822, 'don’t_let_tax_savings_go_unclaimed_description', '<p>If you think your company might be performing work that qualifies for the R&D tax credit, don’t let tax savings go unclaimed—and don’t be deceived by preconceived notions of what R&D is, or which companies can qualify.</p>\r\n<p>Across industries, the possibilities for qualifying activities are out there, and if you’re willing to take a look, you could uncover vital tax savings to reinvest in your business and fuel your next big project. To learn more about the credit and how much you might save, contact us.</p>'),
