(12527, 878, '_energy_efficient_home_credit_net_benefits_title', 'field_61adc4716b831'),
(12528, 878, 'energy_efficient_home_credit_net_benefits_content', '<p>The benefit is equal to $2,000 per qualifying residential unit or dwelling to developers of energy efficient buildings.   Certification fees vary, and are charged on a per-unit basis as each unit has to meet the criteria to qualify. </p>'),
(12529, 878, '_energy_efficient_home_credit_net_benefits_content', 'field_61adc48a6b832'),
(12530, 878, 'energy_efficient_home_credit_net_benefits_data_table', '<thead>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <th scope=\"col\">Qualified Units</th>\r\n    <th scope=\"col\">Credit Amount</th>\r\n    <th scope=\"col\">Fee</th>\r\n    <th scope=\"col\">Net Benefit</th>\r\n  </tr>\r\n</thead>\r\n<tbody>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>50</td>\r\n    <td>$100,000</td>\r\n    <td>$15,000</td>\r\n    <td>$85,000</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n  <tr>\r\n    <td>100</td>\r\n    <td>$200,000</td>\r\n    <td>$27,500</td>\r\n    <td>$172,000</td>\r\n  </tr>\r\n</tbody>'),
(12531, 878, '_energy_efficient_home_credit_net_benefits_data_table', 'field_61adc49b6b833'),
(12532, 764, 'tax_credit_requirements_title', 'Tax Credit Requirements'),
(12533, 764, '_tax_credit_requirements_title', 'field_61adc5c1e0406'),
(12534, 764, 'tax_credit_requirements_content', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Certification must be completed by a licensed, unrelated third-party professional. Our 45L certifications are evaluated, modeled and validated by our engineers. </li>\r\n	<li>When certification is complete, you receive a package with all necessary documentation to sustain the tax credit in case of IRS audit.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(12535, 764, '_tax_credit_requirements_content', 'field_61adc5cbe0407'),
(12536, 764, 'get_started_title', 'Get Started'),
(12537, 764, '_get_started_title', 'field_61adc5dde0408'),
(12538, 764, 'get_started_content', '<p>The process starts with a no-cost review of your construction projects <strong>(in process or completed)</strong>. With a good set of construction plans and project specifications, we determine which units can qualify for these credits. We  discuss with you the necessary next steps to complete certification and documentation as required by the IRS under 45L. </p>\r\n<h3>This process generally takes 30-60 days to complete.</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#\">Request an Estimate</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"#\">Let’s Talk <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right\"></i></a></li>\r\n</ul>'),
(12539, 764, '_get_started_content', 'field_61adc61ce0409'),
