(12801, 914, 'consider_the_example_content', '<p>Acquisition of $4.3M triple net lease big box retail property  - total reclassification falls on the lower end of the benefit range of a typical retail property.</p>\r\n<p>The cost segregation analysis reallocated 24% into shorter life 5 and 15 year property. The overall cost/benefit ratio is 53 to 1.</p>'),
(12802, 914, '_consider_the_example_content', 'field_618f76fbc20af'),
