(15368, 1061, 'challenging_content', 'The challenge many employers will face is not knowing whether they qualify, but rather maximizing their qualified credits. Calculating the maximum credit you or your client are entitled to requires an expert knowledge of the Consolidated Appropriations Act as well as an expert team to make the claiming process effortless.\r\n<h4>Our experts are available to help you manage changes to the CARES Act and calculate exactly how much credit you (or your client) are eligible to claim.</h4>'),
