(15531, 1074, '_care_about_your_clients_title', 'field_61af0de0cdc53'),
(15532, 1074, 'care_about_your_clients_details', '<p>As trusted Advisors, you know your clients’ pain points and work hard to find solutions.However, with dynamic tax policy changes and an increasing demand for tax strategy and big picture planning, it is essential to think outside the box to deliver more and more.</p>\r\n<h3>Let us help you:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Apply cost segregation to accelerate losses and improve current cash flow</li>\r\n	<li>Maximize research and development credit for newly organized technology companies</li>\r\n	<li>Capture tax incentives based on clients’ energy efficiency related efforts</li>\r\n	<li>Implement strategies for clients to get more value out of past real estate projects</li>\r\n	<li>Identify overlooked Employee Retention Credits opportunities</li>\r\n	<li>Review current or prior year capital expenditures of retirement dispositions or repair deductions</li>\r\n</ul>'),
