(15666, 799, 'energy_incentives_details', '<p>Meridian’s energy services team reduces taxes and costs by identifying and documenting Federal, State and Local tax incentives for energy efficiency and cost effective financing. The outcome is enhanced economic viability of renewable solutions.</p>\r\n<h3>Services Include:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"/179d-energy-efficient-building-deduction/\">179D Energy Efficient Building Deduction</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/the-45l-home-tax-credit/\">45L Home Tax Credit</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"#\">Sustainability Consulting</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"#\">Energy Financing Services</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our approach amounts to energy-efficient building solutions that meet your specific needs. We take a value engineering approach to assist you with reducing operating costs, leveraging tax benefits, achieving sustainability goals and improving facilities. We define the pros and cons of various energy solutions, and present them to you in a manner which is easily understood by any financial officer.</p>'),
