(15784, 1092, 'who_we_are_content', '<p>We are experts at identifying every benefit our clients are entitled to in full compliance with current legislation. Most successful entrepreneurs, real estate investors, and CPAs know how to evaluate a deal to recognize its true value.  Meridian’s core mission is to help our clients turn value into growth by uncovering frequently overlooked tax planning strategies to boost cash flow.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>$230M Annual Increased Cash Flow</li>\r\n	<li>32 Year Track Record of Success</li>\r\n	<li>300 Years of combined niche tax experience</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our team of licensed engineers, tax attorneys, accounting and construction professionals provides tenured experience in depreciation, valuation, research and development credits, and sustainability incentives.</p>'),
(15785, 1092, '_who_we_are_content', 'field_61ae065e38c3c'),
