inancialsolutions/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/value1.png\" alt=\"\" /> Partnership</h3>\r\n<p>Collaboration for mutual benefit with our clients and within is fundamental to delivering lasting performance through mutual growth.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"principle-block\" el_class=\"custom_inner_content\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>3 Key Principles of Our Win-Win Approach</h2>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"box\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"22\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]We’re a dynamic organization that values and rewards ideas.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"box\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"24\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]We foster a culture of flexibility with an emphasis on results and collaboration.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"box\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"23\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]Our partnerships are based on mutual trust and sharing of fundamental values.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text el_class=\"join-team\"]<a href=\"#\">Join our team</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"top_partner\"][vc_column][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"custom-testimonials\" el_class=\"custom_inner_content\" css=\".vc_custom_1633441878561{background-image: url(http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/testibg.png?id=41) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inn