(465, 1, '2021-11-09 09:20:13', '2021-11-09 09:20:13', '<p>[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"who-block\" el_class=\"custom_inner_content\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text-panel\"]</p>\r\n<h2>Who we are</h2>\r\n<p>We are experts at identifying every benefit our clients are entitled to in full compliance with current legislation.</p>\r\n<p>Most successful entrepreneurs, real estate investors, and CPAs know how to evaluate a deal to recognize its true value.  Meridian’s core mission is to help our clients turn value into growth by uncovering frequently overlooked tax planning strategies to boost cash flow.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>$230M Annual Increased Cash Flow</li>\r\n<li>32 Year Track Record of Success</li>\r\n<li>300 Years of combined niche tax experience</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our team of licensed engineers, tax attorneys, accounting and construction professionals provides tenured experience in depreciation, valuation, research and development credits, and sustainability incentives.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"11\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"right\" el_class=\"who-img\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id=\"client-block\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"18\" img_size=\"full\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"text-panel\"]</p>\r\n<h2>Who we Serve</h2>\r\n<h3>Meridian is a trusted resource to hundreds of CPAs nationwide.</h3>\r\n<h4>Our Clients Included:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Major developers</li>\r\n<li>First-time real estate investors</li>\r\n<li>Public companies</li>\r\n<li>Software businesses, including start-ups</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"service-block\" el_class=\"custom_inner_content\" css=\".vc_custom_1633439561086{background-image: url(http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/servicebg.jpg?id=34) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"7/12\"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>Services</h2>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"5/12\"][vc_single_image image=\"30\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"right\" el_class=\"img-block\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"our-value\" el_class=\"custom_inner_content\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>our founding values</h2>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"box\"]</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/value1.png\" alt=\"\" /> Integrity</h3>\r\n<p>We are honest and forthright in all our relationships. Building trust builds a better company. [/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"box\"]</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/value1.png\" alt=\"\" /> Accountability</h3>\r\n<p>Each of us is responsible for our words, actions, and results. We strive to not simply meet, but to exceed expectations.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"box\"]</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/value1.png\" alt=\"\" /> Hard Work</h3>\r\n<p>Together, we are relentless in the pursuit of excellence to support each other and deliver the best quality products and services.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text el_class=\"box\"]</p>\r\n<h3><img src=\"http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/value1.png\" alt=\"\" /> Partnership</h3>\r\n<p>Collaboration for mutual benefit with our clients and within is fundamental to delivering lasting performance through mutual growth.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"principle-block\" el_class=\"custom_inner_content\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h2>3 Key Principles of Our Win-Win Approach</h2>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"box\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"22\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]We’re a dynamic organization that values and rewards ideas.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"box\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"24\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]We foster a culture of flexibility with an emphasis on results and collaboration.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class=\"box\" width=\"1/3\"][vc_single_image image=\"23\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\"][vc_column_text]Our partnerships are based on mutual trust and sharing of fundamental values.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text el_class=\"join-team\"]<a href=\"#\">Join our team</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"top_partner\"][vc_column][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" el_id=\"custom-testimonials\" el_class=\"custom_inner_content\" css=\".vc_custom_1633441878561{background-image: url(http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/testibg.png?id=41) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_raw_html]JTVCdGVzdGltb25pYWxfc2hvcnRjb2RlJTVE[/vc_raw_html][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>\r\n', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '8-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-11-09 09:20:13', '2021-11-09 09:20:13', '', 8, 'http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/?p=465', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
