(500, 1, '2021-11-11 11:05:35', '2021-11-11 11:05:35', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Engineering Firm</li>\r\n	<li>$400k in R&D Tax Credits</li>\r\n        <li><span>Annual Revenue:</span> $38M</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>This civil and structural engineering firm designs bridges, buildings and otherstructures. In one qualifying project, the company designed a building with its ownwater reclamation facility beneathanunderground parking garage. Their design had to comply with stringent building codes to protect against earthquakes and other environmental factors. The city would not allow any water runoff, and the utility system was at capacity.Therefore, the building could not be connected to the city sewer system. The company modeled many different designsto land on one that met allenvironmental and code qualifications.</p>', 'Engineering firm receives $400,000 in tax credits', 'This civil and structural engineering firm designs bridges, buildings and otherstructures. In one qualifying project, the company designed a building with its ownwater reclamation facility beneathanunderground parking garage', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'engineering-firm-receives-400000-in-tax-credits', '', '', '2021-11-24 10:46:36', '2021-11-24 10:46:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/?post_type=studies&#038;p=500', 0, 'studies', '', 0),
(501, 1, '2021-11-11 11:07:34', '2021-11-11 11:07:34', '<ul>\r\n    <li>Food Processor</li>\r\n    <li>$800k in R&D Tax Credits</li>\r\n    <li><span>Annual Revenue:</span> $160M</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>This food processer made salad dressing, mayonnaise and other condiments. The companywanted to expand their product line to include new flavors,and develop ahealth conscious product line of allergen and corn syrup-free products. Their staff reformulated each recipe to remove gluten, corn syrup, egg andother ingredients, but maintain the same quality and taste. After trials werecompleted, some of the new recipe formulations also required the company toredesign the production process and acquire additional processing equipment. Wage and materialexpenses for these developments were included to calculate their research credit.</p>', 'Food Processor receives $800,000 in Tax Credits', 'This food processer made salad dressing, mayonnaise and other condiments. The companywanted to expand their product line to include new flavors,and develop ahealth conscious product line of allergen and corn syrup-free products.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'food-processor-receives-800000-in-tax-credits', '', '', '2021-11-24 10:46:19', '2021-11-24 10:46:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/?post_type=studies&#038;p=501', 0, 'studies', '', 0),
(502, 1, '2021-11-11 11:09:08', '2021-11-11 11:09:08', '<ul>\r\n    <li>Custom Machinery Manufacturer</li>\r\n    <li>$1.1M in R&D Tax Credits</li>\r\n    <li><span>Annual Revenue:</span> $12M</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>This manufacturer designed custom machines to fold cardboard into customshapedand sized boxes. Company engineers, mechanics, and other professionalsdesigned and built each one to client specifications. Eachmachine was unique and qualified as a prototype, allowing the entire cost to be included as a qualified expense for tax credit.</p>', 'Custom machinery manufacturer receives $1.1M in tax credits.', 'This manufacturer designed custom machines to fold cardboard into customshapedand sized boxes. Company engineers, mechanics, and other professionalsdesigned and built each one to client specifications.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'custom-machinery-manufacturer-receives-1-1m-in-tax-credits', '', '', '2021-11-24 10:46:09', '2021-11-24 10:46:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/?post_type=studies&#038;p=502', 0, 'studies', '', 0),
(503, 1, '2021-11-11 11:10:08', '2021-11-11 11:10:08', '<ul>\r\n    <li>Start-Up App Developer</li>\r\n    <li>$1.2M in R&D Tax Credits</li>\r\n    <li><span>Annual Revenue:</span> $800K</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>This start-up company developed custom apps for small banking, insurance, andother financial service providers. While the company was experiencing losses (not payingincome tax), they reduced their payroll taxes by $250k per year. Remaining credits were carried forward to future years. For 2019, they are expectingto be profitable, and will apply the remaining credits and 2019 credit against anyincome tax owed for 2019.</p>', 'Start-up Company offsets payroll taxes by $250,000 a year', 'This start-up company developed custom apps for small banking, insurance, andother financial service providers. While the company was experiencing losses (not payingincome tax), they reduced their payroll taxes by $250k per year.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'start-up-company-offsets-payroll-taxes-by-250000-a-year', '', '', '2021-11-24 10:45:56', '2021-11-24 10:45:56', '', 0, 'http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/?post_type=studies&#038;p=503', 0, 'studies', '', 0),
(504, 1, '2021-11-11 11:11:20', '2021-11-11 11:11:20', '<ul>\r\n    <li>Mold Tool and Die</li>\r\n    <li>$3.2M in R&D Tax Credits</li>\r\n    <li><span>Annual Revenue:</span> $132M</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our client extruded aluminum and other metal alloys for various uses includingwindow frames, furniture, marine products and more. With each new extruded itemthey produced, the client designed and developed molds, tools,dies and other fixtures. Each of these newly designed items had to be developed,“worked,” and tested. Materials for these items, as well as the raw supplymaterials used to test the new designs, were includable expenses along with thewages of personnel who worked on these projects.</p>', 'Tool & Die company receives $3.2M in tax credits.', 'Our client extruded aluminum and other metal alloys for various uses includingwindow frames, furniture, marine products and more. With each new extruded itemthey produced, the client designed and developed molds, tools,dies and other fixtures. ', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tool-die-company-receives-3-2m-in-tax-credits', '', '', '2021-11-24 10:45:28', '2021-11-24 10:45:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/meridianfinancialsolutions/?post_type=studies&#038;p=504', 0, 'studies', '', 0),
